import { View, Text, Image, TouchableOpacity } from 'react-native'

import { SafeAreaView } from 'react-native-safe-area-context'
import { COLORS, icons } from '../constants';

const Profile = () => {

            height: 50}}>Profile

          marginLeft:10,
          marginRight:10,
          height:100,
          borderRadius:10

            marginLeft:15

              fontSize:20, 
              fontWeight:'bold',
              color:"white"
            }}>Iyon Setiawan S.Sos</Text>

              fontSize:12, 
              color:"white"
            }}>19701028 2001021 102</Text>
          </View>

          }}>

        </View>
        </TouchableOpacity>

          backgroundColor:COLORS.white,
          padding:10,
          marginTop:15,
          marginRight:10,
          marginLeft:10,
          height:80,
          borderRadius:10,
        }}>
          <Image
            source={icons.Logout}

export default Profile
